      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a benchmark example of JDM engineering, preserved in showroom condition. Under the hood, the 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six remains entirely stock, delivering smooth, sequential boost with factory-spec compression across all cylinders. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis retains its structural rigidity with original double-wishbone suspension components and four-piston brake calipers that show no signs of thermal stress. Finished in its original factory coat with a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade specimen for the serious purist.",
